AAAAAAADbY/pbdljwEgTwE/s1600/%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2589%25AE%25E5%25A6%2596%25E8%2589%25B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-kWkVsUgC2RU%2FVZTfFwZMQ-I%2FAAAAAAAADbY%2FpbdljwEgTwE%2Fs1600%2F%2525E5%2525A4%2525A7%2525E5%2525AA%2525BD%2525E5%25259C%252598%2525E6%252589%252593%2525E6%252589%2525AE%2525E5%2525A6%252596%2525E8%252589%2525B7.jpg&h=3a61cda1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc59dd287d08b27385089ae9080885583e162445","tid":153384,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家星期六、日盡可能都唔出旺角。<br />\n<br />\n我退一百步黎講，唱歌無問題啊，但有一班老中廢、蝗聽歌圍到個圈圍足成條馬路，叫人點行呀～ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行女人街仲暢通過佢～</blockquote><br />\n有d跳撚埋舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戶外夜總會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-kWkVsUgC2RU/VZTfFwZMQ-I/AAAAAAAADbY/pbdljwEgTwE/s1600/%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2589%25AE%25E5%25A6%2596%25E8%2589%25B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-kWkVsUgC2RU%2FVZTfFwZMQ-I%2FAAAAAAAADbY%2FpbdljwEgTwE%2Fs1600%2F%2525E5%2525A4%2525A7%2525E5%2525AA%2525BD%2525E5%25259C%252598%2525E6%252589%252593%2525E6%252589%2525AE%2525E5%2525A6%252596%2525E8%252589%2525B7.jpg&h=3a61cda1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所我先話又係領展的好事囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋邨d茶樓仲有得跳舞咪唔會出黎旺角囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8492e183de5c6a2732a9e3f6a034e6eaa752d7bb","tid":153384,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下班左膠黃絲<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/jmc.hksyu.edu/shuo/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fjmc.hksyu.edu%2Fshuo%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2F018.jpg&h=37c68a18&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好矛盾，我都覺得要有空間比人發展唔同類型既藝術，香港的確有好多有質素既街頭音樂人，但絕對唔係旺角呢班。<br />\n<br />\n如果英國佬時期，可能可以搞一個委員會去處理、發牌，可以係質素同空間兩者之間取得平衡，但今時今日個政府信唔過，亦無咁既政治智慧係任何事上搵平衡點，所以先會搞成所有事非黑即白、兩元對立。"},{"pid":"74d53796266454a4dd7edb3c99dce2da7f64f543","tid":153384,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"同埋大家小心，如果最後因爲嘈同阻街影響所以取消呢一類行人路表演，之後政府能夠大條道理路唔比呢一類街頭表演係香港出現。最大問題係表演者令人反感唔係街頭表演令人反感。解決方法我諗為係要杜絕霸位買位，令其他人有機會使用，自然無人睇既表戲淘汰。"},{"pid":"1dff9558ec3ff39c2abb61acb6dc183bb57e2fa1","tid":153384,"uid":4849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"當年掟鏹水嗰個真係先驅"},{"pid":"5eb1cd61054a3efa8a45f6c19704778728fff50a","tid":153384,"uid":22121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80df60c845b3fa7f2ca7d4c0771cb76f0f3cad31","tid":153384,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年掟鏹水嗰個真係先驅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f976f41fcf8ea6bcb925761a14f970bf4d7c42","tid":153384,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"果d仆街垃圾廢老廢中成撚日係求鳩叫，跳鳩舞，<br />\n人地外國遊客區就表演真正既藝術，雜耍，<br />\n外國人去一個地方就係睇呢d得到一對一個城市既形象，<br />\n呢班撚屌就破壞香港，令到外國人覺得香港同蝗國一撚樣，<br />\n仲要嘈住本地既居民，<br />\n快撚d去投胎，下世去大陸飲污水，吸廢氣啦"},{"pid":"a8e6cc7cbf91aad876b8357dd77ce1db916f7548","tid":153384,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家星期六、日盡可能都唔出旺角。<br />\n<br />\n我退一百步黎講，唱歌無問題啊，但有一班老中廢、蝗聽歌圍到個圈圍足成條馬路，叫人點行呀～ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行女人街仲暢通過佢～</blockquote><br />\n有d跳撚埋舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戶外夜總會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.co